data.description: 12-13-23 - Contract Accepted. Price Reduced!! Ask about the Assumable Loan at 2.63% that you don't need to be a veteran to qualify! A home like this doesn't come along very often.  Located in the heart of Castle Rock, with views of "The Rock" you will love this great ranch home situated on a  great corner lot on a cul-de-sac. Also, this neighborhood has NO HOA! When you enter the home you will get a feel of true one-level living with vaulted ceilings and plenty of space for entertaining. The open kitchen has been updated with quartz countertops and tile backsplash, and features an island, pantry and eat-in dining area. The living room and formal dining area affords plenty of options with flexible space. The main floor primary bedroom has vaulted ceilings, a fireplace and features a 5-piece bath, including a jacuzzi tub, oversized shower and two closets. The main floor front bedroom is ideal for an office or guest room with a shared bath. The downstairs family room is an expansive space that includes a great bar area and room for all the gatherings you can imagine. The two lower bedrooms are large and are served by their own 3/4 bath with a relaxing jacuzzi tub. Outside you have a large fenced-in yard with wrap-around Trex deck, patios, fire pit and artificial turf for easy maintenance. There also is a large storage shed. The Solar Panel System was installed in 2020, is PAID OFF, and consists of 33 Panels with a 13,398 kWh capacity. The 3-car garage is large with a dedicated 220V system. Sellers are offering a $5,000 carpet allowance at closing. This house comes with a locked in REDUCED RATE as low as 6.625% through List & Lock™. This is a seller paid rate-buydown that reduces the buyer’s interest rate and monthly payment. Terms apply, see disclosures for more information. Put it all together and you will be glad to call this your home.
